Package: yamlscript
Type: Package
Title: Load YAML Files with Optional YS Functional Programming
Version: 0.2.28
Author: Ingy dot Net
Maintainer: Ingy dot Net <ingy@ingy.net>
Description: Load YAML files that may use YS (YAMLScript) functional
    programming capabilities. A drop-in replacement for your current
    YAML loader, binding to the libys shared library.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: jsonlite
NeedsCompilation: yes
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://yamlscript.org
BugReports: https://github.com/yaml/yamlscript/issues
